# ============================================================
# E7 Activity — Assertions of Jurisdiction
# Each assertion links: who asserted (E74 Group), where (E93
# Presence for the spatial extent), when (E52 Time-Span), and
# which Indigenous territories (E53 Place) were affected.
# These are assertions by European/settler powers. They do not
# represent consent, cession, or effective control over
# Indigenous territories. Effective Indigenous governance
# persisted well beyond these assertion dates in many regions.
# ============================================================

